The transportId property of the {{domxref("RTCRemoteOutboundRtpStreamStats")}} dictionary is a string that uniquely identifies the object from which the statistics contained in the {{domxref("RTCTransportStats")}} properties in the {{domxref("RTCStatsReport")}}.
